strings: <voice_0x01001857><se_low>The key: But! You, yes, I remember... You are a courageous person and I present to you the magic mirror of nature.
<voice_0x01001858><se_low>The key: What brings you here... I want to share an important fact.
Show me King Clavis' Argon Ring.
<voice_0x01001859><se_low>The key: very crazy! If you don't say anything, you can just leave him alone. It may not look like it, but it is actually quite busy.
<voice_0x0100185A><se_low>The key: This organ plays in your heart. What’s wrong with you?
<voice_0x0100185B><se_low>The key: Hmm... your story disappointed me too...
<voice_0x0100185C><se_low>The key: You look like the son of Eltree.
<voice_0x0100185D><se_low>The key: Is there another way to understand what I'm talking about?
<voice_0x0100185E><se_low>The key: expression. If my brother had not left after your mother, he would still be King of Aragon.
<voice_0x0100185F><se_low>The key: And if you were born a prince, I believe that tomorrow you will marry Princess Medea...
<voice_0x01001860><se_low>The key: But that's just guesswork.
<voice_0x01001861><se_low>The key: If a new heir emerges this evening, the whole country will be cremated. I cannot verify your request.
<voice_0x01001862><se_low>The key: ...don't feel sorry for me if you're thinking of closing this question. Come
<voice_0x01001863><se_low>The key: Still in there, right? Anything you want to say?
<voice_0x01001877><se_low>The key: Where does the new heir to the throne come from? Chaos will rule the earth. so you can see
<voice_0x01001878><se_low>The key: doubt your intent
<voice_0x01001879><se_low>The key: But what is the use of wearing a ring now? Could Chalmers not marry Princess Medea?
<voice_0x0100187A><se_low>The key: I admit he was immature and reckless at times.
<voice_0x0100187B><se_low>The key: But I want to marry a beautiful woman like my dad and live happily ever after.
<voice_0x0100187C><se_low>The key: He said that he has been on good terms with the princess since he was a child.
<voice_0x0100187D><se_low>The key: do you have any feelings for him?
<voice_0x0100187E><se_low>The key: Deadline So... can I ask her to marry me?
<voice_0x0100187F><se_low>The key: Now, if you want to laugh at me, I'll tell you about my father and my grandfather from Semler. when i was just a little prince
<voice_0x01001880><se_low>The key: Traveling around the world, he met Princess Tradden and fell in love with her at a young age.
<voice_0x01001881><se_low>The key: Unfortunately for the young couple, the relationship between Argonia and Truden was strained at the time.
<voice_0x01001882><se_low>The key: ...and her father's hopes of marrying the princess were dashed by fierce opposition from the two dynasties.
<voice_0x01001883><se_low>The key: Couples who cannot be together One day your child will get married. bound by the promise of love
<voice_0x01001884><se_low>The key: His father, however, had a son with the Princess Troday.
<voice_0x01001885><se_low>The key: I left without knowing my dream.
<voice_0x01001886><se_low>The key: That's why we keep our promises to ourselves.
<voice_0x01001887><se_low>The key: That is why I recommend Princess Medea to wear the amulet.
<voice_0x01001888><se_low>The key: I could not change my mind after fulfilling the wishes of King Trudeau and I would not leave my father even if I could.
<voice_0x01001889><se_low>The key: I really don't like your solution. But at least I figured it out... That's it. Can you go?
<voice_0x0100188A><se_low>The key: Goddess of beauty, do you think that other women get more attention?
<voice_0x0100188B><se_low>The key: ...do you love someone enough to get married?
<voice_0x0100188C><se_low>The key: What are you doing right now
<voice_0x0100188D><se_low>The key: Your relationship is a flip side. So what caused problems between Shamels and Maddy?
<voice_0x0100188E><se_low>The key: Don't you understand the consequences of your actions?
<voice_0x0100188F><se_low>The key: With this ring he shows El Tri, the son of my brother.
<voice_0x01001890><se_low>The key: what you don't see Now you have the right to marry Princess Medea!
<voice_0x01001891><se_low>The key: Tell me, what do you think will happen if he finds out that you refused to find a mate with your camel?
<voice_0x01001892><se_low>The key: I assure you this will not cancel the wedding or embarrass the little ones.
<voice_0x01001893><se_low>The key: There was no dispute about the rightful heir to the throne!
<voice_0x01001894><se_low>The key: Have you ever wondered how damaging your pointless delusions can be?
<voice_0x01001895><se_low>The key: I do not have anything to say. to be mine
<voice_0x01001896><se_low>The key: Do you want to admit this?
<voice_0x01001897><se_low>The key: Please try again, is it good?
<voice_0x01001898><se_low>The key: Do you like the Princess Medea?
